<p itemprop="description">今天是周日啦，追着甜甜爱情的网剧《离人心上》，再随眼缘从Appstore里选了《艾莎的国度》，开启了我废柴的一天。下这个<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/youxi/" target="_blank">游戏</a>也是因为看到评论挺逗的，有玩家说是这个游戏可以改名叫“奸商模拟器”了“人造景点一条龙宰客服务”了真是给我逗笑了，决定下了尝试一下。<img alt="在游戏里当“奸商”  体会别样的模拟经营" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/184.gif" class="face" /> </p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ar0nezmg/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="在游戏里当“奸商”  体会别样的模拟经营" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/06/5f5446b77e3bc3899.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">这篇文章是我边玩边写的，看起来是很流水账的~</p><p itemprop="description">好啦，不多说，下好游戏之后就进入游戏啦 ！</p><dir><span class="embed-card main-site " style=""><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'‎App Store上的“艾丽莎的国度”','id':'ar0nezmg' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'Apple Store', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'apple.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/b81f6ed780f09cb8/ca_bb_yc_5716_71064435_13107_0_1353_0"  rel="nofollow" ><img ol  alt="在游戏里当“奸商”  体会别样的模拟经营" class="res_smzdm" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202009/06/5f5438a06cc799149.png_a200.jpg"/></a></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'‎App Store上的“艾丽莎的国度”','id':'ar0nezmg' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'Apple Store', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'apple.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/b81f6ed780